    "title": "Principal Data Architect",
    "excerpt": "<p>Under the general direction of the Deputy Director, Data Operations Strategy, the Principal Data Architect serves as the Office of Data &amp; Innovation’s (ODI) primary technical authority for data engineering platforms and services and is responsible for defining and maintaining technical policies, standards, and architectural frameworks that govern ODI’s data engineering work. The Principal Data &#8230; <a title=\"Principal Data Architect\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/join-us/principal-data-architect/\" aria-label=\"More on Principal Data Architect\">Read more</a></p>\n",
